<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT84">
<l>pitiru maṉamilēṉ piññakaṉ ṟaṉṉō</l>
<l>ṭetirva ṉavaṉeṉakku nērā ṉatiruṅ</l>
<l>kaḻaṟkāla maṉṉaṉaiyē kaṇṇaṉaiyē nāḷun</l>
<l>toḻuṅkātaṟ pūṇṭēṉ toḻil.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I who bear love—[so that my] occupation is to always worship</l>
<l>the King with feet [adorned with] resounding anklets, Kṛṣṇa—</l>
<l>do not have a scattered mind.</l>
<l>I rival Śiva [in terms of knowledge but] he is no match for me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
